title: Ensiferum - 10th Anniversary Live - DVDmkv-By_Golden_Commando
description:
10th Anniversary Live is a live performance DVD celebrating the 10th anniversary of the viking/folk metal band Ensiferum. 
It was filmed on New Year's Eve, 2005 at the music hall Nosturi in Helsinki, Finland.

Released June 28, 2006 
Length: 104:13 
Label: Spinefarm 
File:mkv
